{"tid":1192783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"林芷晴，請你入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-08T15:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T00:29:04.000Z","uid":69542,"like":3,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0079939a868107cd462e68efdab5ff3b0a92b85b","tid":1192783,"uid":69542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"我知你係連登妹，有啲野想同你講。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你逼我儲錢，廿幾歲人月月清，搵幾多洗幾多，諗返起都覺得on9，你話咁大個人少少儲蓄都冇，邊個肯嫁俾你？<br />\n<br />\n其實好啱，現實真係冇幾個，同你捱冇問題，但至少似返個人，識思考嘅人，儲錢姐，好基本。<br />\n<br />\n請大家珍惜一個會逼你儲錢嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n林芷晴，我食硬你，請你以後幫個手，睇住我盤數，謝謝。"},{"pid":"b410d4e2c3dc2b321eb84c45042520e1e92e506e","tid":1192783,"uid":143033,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03985ceecc14eb028dddcced55b4c25a7b7eafe3","tid":1192783,"uid":52230,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"唔係林芷晴但睇完濕左...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244fd56c4a8edd09a1ad491ac2cae6020be70e8f","tid":1192783,"uid":248275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb69e9d53e38f75432b40ee4623e7589c7e11fc1","tid":1192783,"uid":38358,"like":4,"dislik